title: Hour 3 - Doug Gottlieb & TJ Houshmandzadeh Guest Hosting
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Doug Gottlieb & TJ Houshmandzadeh Guest Hosting
description:
With Doug and TJ filling in for Dan. Doug and TJ discuss the likelihood of the Lakers trading for Kyrie Irving and if Russell Westbrook is enough to get it done.  ZaK Keefer covers the Colts for The Athletic, he joins Doug and TJ to talk about his new podcast series featuring the life and career of Andrew Luck.  Doug and TJ talks about what is going to happen with the NFL's Sunday Ticket Package.  

#DougGottliebShow   #UpOnGame 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
